ne savent pas danser ?

127
00:06:14,775 --> 00:06:16,963
- Je m'appelle Renee.
- Daniel.

128
00:06:17,065 --> 00:06:18,830
Meade. Je sais.

129
00:06:18,938 --> 00:06:20,400
